00:16:44,250 --> 00:16:58,930
And here's the scheme that connects with lab signal generator and controls power key.

115
00:16:58,930 --> 00:17:04,310
See what isolation control transformer looks like.

116
00:17:05,150 --> 00:17:06,890
Wound immediately in two wires.

