141
00:19:30,550 --> 00:19:36,770
Can buy and it very well fits on surface of these chips.

142
00:19:37,930 --> 00:19:43,070
Well and basically, nothing super-complex here.

143
00:19:44,310 --> 00:19:51,450
Visible that zener diodes I raised higher because in experiments anything can happen.

144
