145
00:19:57,310 --> 00:20:06,930
Therefore, to not disassemble whole circuit, enough to just clip wires with little pieces and solder new zener diodes here.

146
00:20:06,950 --> 00:20:09,170
Well, circuit again operational.

147
00:20:09,750 --> 00:20:18,890
With key blowing nothing happens to driver, to transformer, much less to control block.

148
00:20:19,750 --> 00:20:21,690
Circuit reliably isolated.

149
00:20:25,300 --> 00:20:27,240
Assembled circuit for demonstration.

